[White nose syndrome has taken a toll on many bat populations,
especially the little brown bat. This article does not tell us what
type of bat was affected.

Different areas tend to have different bats and there are several
species that have been affected. If someone knows which bats are
affected, it would be nice to know. - Mod.TG]

